{"tid":2408323,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–透視癌細胞","createTime":"2021-02-14T22:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T02:53:14.000Z","uid":38861,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"90df9d088942dc0f6d9bd62b110b35bf9d8cb8ab","tid":2408323,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T22:02:38.000Z","msg":"癌細胞轉移，即是從原來的位置轉移到另一地方。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZMLFJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZMLFJg.jpg&h=18424379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利用老鼠作為癌細胞轉移研究的話，科學家又是如何得知癌細胞是否有出現轉移的過程，以及所轉移的地方呢?<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）探知癌細胞轉移而又不需殺害老鼠的其中一道手段，就是藉助螢火蟲的螢光素酶幫助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7tpYggE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7tpYggE.jpg&h=ac151106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n螢光素酶(Luciferase)能夠將螢光素(Luciferin)轉化成為另一物質，同時亦會發出螢光。<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，利用分子生物學技術強迫癌細胞表達螢光素酶的話，當他們遇上螢光素的時候，便會在其所在的位置發出螢光。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）往老鼠移植含螢光素酶的癌細胞，到達需要進行研究時間的時候便為牠們注射Luciferin，Luciferin會經由血液循環系統走遍全身，過一段時間後再對牠們進行麻醉，並用儀器探測螢光，便可以得知癌細胞的大小及所在位置。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FPoBNot.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFPoBNot.png&h=678382ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將右圖對比左圖，便可清晰得知右圖的癌細胞出現了轉移。將此螢光方法配合藥物或基因改造手段，便可得知所對應的醫學方法能否修成正果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=cc8bbf56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=888ffe2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27974793/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F27974793%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=e1680fff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27974793/</a>"},{"pid":"3028622548b74524cd0764c863ffc997be334b36","tid":2408323,"uid":199112,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T22:03:23.000Z","msg":"頭香"},{"pid":"a04a239b15224e929c9477d43f64999b879a15d5","tid":2408323,"uid":380296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T22:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96951449617e596a4a12690c14190c134620d4b","tid":2408323,"uid":38861,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"3028622548b74524cd0764c863ffc997be334b36","tid":2408323,"uid":199112,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T22:03:23.000Z","msg":"頭香"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T22:04:27.000Z","msg":"頭香係大陸用語<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac982e3d71f834f00b764f89b2356983d9afb34","tid":2408323,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T22:04:42.000Z","